{"tid":2117462,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港恒生大學BBA-MGT 裝備充足 畢業生就業理想","createTime":"2020-07-21T01:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T19:36:50.000Z","uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7011ad82c57c160df8059428bd03cda102c2a116","tid":2117462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:08:44.000Z","msg":"香港恒生大學（恒大）管理學系強調以人為本，為培育未來青年領袖作出貢獻，其中的「管理學工商管理學士課程」（BBA-MGT），致力協助學生裝備自我、發揮所長、開展理想事業。<br />\n<br />\n 根據恒大學生事務處的畢業生就業調查，首屆BBA-MGT畢業生的就業率達<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">100%</span></span>，是恒大畢業生唯一達至全體就業的學士課程，反映BBA-MGT畢業生在就業市場上具備競爭力。<br />\n<br />\nBBA-MGT課程博雅和專業並重，除管理學、商業學和基礎教育的必修科目之外，本課程亦包涵選修科目，佔全部科目的37.5%，比例較一般課程高，讓學生可以按照自己的興趣、能力和事業抱負選修適合自己的科目，提升個人成長的可塑性和選擇事業的靈活性。"},{"pid":"7d47a9694930e7fdb1f2b3ccb80faa849fdda085","tid":2117462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:08:54.000Z","msg":"BBA-MGT提供不少必修和選修科目，能提升同學的軟技巧，例如組織行為、管理技巧和衝突管理等。課程亦著重實習工作的培訓，過去兩年共有120位學生參與實習工作，實習地點包括本地及內地、英國、新加坡和美國等，更有同學獲得在跨國企業如寶馬汽車公司（BMW）和L&rsquo;Oreal的實習機會，其所獲的經驗能增加學生求職成功的機會。"},{"pid":"996f3ca04eca670392b47e5372270a005c047817","tid":2117462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:09:16.000Z","msg":"課程同時重視學生對行業或企業知識的掌握，每個學期皆會舉辦三至四次講座，如<span class=\"red\"><strong>營商經驗分享會</strong></span>和客席講座等，邀請來自各界別的業內人仕及學者作分享，讓學生了解業界最新發展，為將來做好準備。"},{"pid":"a64e132c3d6c919546e637c81ad206696bbed1f5","tid":2117462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"我恆又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4aa65190e3e08684e0046f7240b1311310a8bad","tid":2117462,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"就業率達100%<br />\n保險 地產 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHku都冇可能100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcae3343acfeab9980998ac78df79f174bab8d6","tid":2117462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4aa65190e3e08684e0046f7240b1311310a8bad","tid":2117462,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"就業率達100%<br />\n保險 地產 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHku都冇可能100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:12:00.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇吓有冇恆大學生分享下<br />\n如果屬實 恆大或成最大贏家<br />\nhsu終於超越hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ef6827da7c2dc6e6f38a0c3928064835734981","tid":2117462,"uid":32345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4aa65190e3e08684e0046f7240b1311310a8bad","tid":2117462,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"就業率達100%<br />\n保險 地產 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHku都冇可能100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"因為hku果D係唔洗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0e8a4c62631c342ec5c58b6e49576bc033192e","tid":2117462,"uid":363503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T19:36:50.000Z","msg":"[長文慎入][恒大樹大請入]識得黑警個仔Matthew Law同佢老死陳懷謙既麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n恒大手足請睇路"}]}